segments and intersections. For this purpose the existing 2012 PM peak hour traffic
data was used with existing lane configuration. FIU experiences the highest volume of
traffic during the PM peak period as many part-time students commute to/from
campus during this period. The level of service (LOS) results obtained is indicative of
